description:
This is a 23 minute workout called '20 min STANDING DUMBBELL WORKOUT | Full Body | Sculpt and Strengthen | Warm Up + Cool Down Included' from the channel fitbymik.
The workout falls under Strength/Weight workout.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
You'll need Weights for this workout.
The workout has a The Meditative Grind and The Progression Quest vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light and Moderate.
